g.text: Our Private Room Fee is $100.00 (Three Hours)
The number of guests for your event will be conﬁrmed one week before the event date.
Final Payment is due one week before the event date.
Payments can be made in Cash or Personal or Business Check. If the event is Tax Exempt, please email cerﬁcate to
Deposits are required to secure your event date. Your deposit is nonrefundable if your reservaon is cancelled 8 weeks prior to
your date. If we do not receive a deposit within one week of booking the event, we will release the date.
DTO will ID all guests if necessary and will deny serving alcohol to any persons intoxicated.
DTO does not allow outside Beverages OR Alcohol in our establishment.
Décor’ – No Tacks OR Tape on Walls OR Ceiling.
There is a $50.00 charge for use of confe for décor.
DTO has the right to charge for any obvious damage or necessary repairs caused at your event.
Please do not hesitate to call with any quesons.
